#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:855,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:1287, ../includes/i18n.php:855,
#: ../includes/i18n.php:1287
msgid "Offset key"
msgstr "Offset-Schlüssel"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:856,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:1288, ../includes/i18n.php:856,
#: ../includes/i18n.php:1288
msgid ""
"Set the key you used for the offset. Example: limit = 20 set on query "
"parameter, Page parameter is \"skip\", set this offset key as \"limit\". "
"Clicking page 3 on the pagination element will generate the final URL as "
"https://api.example.com/endpoint?skip=40&limit=20"
msgstr ""
"Lege den Schlüssel fest, den du für den Versatz verwendet hast. Beispiel: "
"Limit = 20 im Abfrageparameter, Seitenparameter ist \"Skip\", setze diesen "
"Offset-Schlüssel als \"Limit\". Wenn du auf Seite 3 des Paginierungselements "
"klickst, wird die endgültige URL als https://api.example.com/endpoint?"
"skip=40&limit=20 generiert"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:857,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:1289, ../includes/i18n.php:857,
#: ../includes/i18n.php:1289
