#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:1290, ../includes/i18n.php:858,
#: ../includes/i18n.php:1290
msgid ""
"Where you defined the offset key. Bricks will retrieve the value from there."
msgstr ""
"Wo du den Offset-Schlüssel definiert hast. Bricks wird den Wert von dort "
"abrufen."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:859,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/i18n.php:1295, ../includes/i18n.php:859,
#: ../includes/i18n.php:1295
