msgid "Email content"
msgstr "E-Mail-Inhalt"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:957,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/form.php:1334,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/elements/form.php:1497,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:957,
#: ../includes/elements/form.php:1334, ../includes/elements/form.php:1497
msgid "HTML email"
msgstr "HTML-E-Mail"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:967,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:967
msgid ""
"Password protection limits access to content on the rendered frontend only. "
"It does not restrict alternative access methods (e.g. REST API). For "
"sensitive data, consider stricter security controls."
msgstr ""
"Der Passwortschutz beschränkt den Zugriff auf Inhalte nur im gerenderten "
"Frontend. Er schränkt alternative Zugriffsmethoden (z.B. REST API) nicht "
"ein. Erwäge für sensible Daten strengere Sicherheitskontrollen."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:977,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:977
msgid "Orphaned elements"
msgstr "Verwaiste Elemente"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:982,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:982
msgid "Check for orphaned elements on builder save"
msgstr "Auf verwaiste Elemente beim Speichern des Builders prüfen"

#. translators: %1$s: Link to orphaned elements documentation, %2$s: URL parameter
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:987,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:987
msgid ""
"Checks for %1$s on builder save to check for orphaned elements. Always "
"checked on load regardless of this setting. Can also be manually enabled by "
"adding %2$s to the builder URL."
msgstr ""
"Prüft auf %1$s beim Speichern des Builders, um verwaiste Elemente zu finden. "
"Wird unabhängig von dieser Einstellung immer beim Laden geprüft. Kann auch "
"manuell aktiviert werden, indem %2$s zur Builder-URL hinzugefügt wird."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:997,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:997
msgid "Scan your site for orphaned elements that may cause issues."
msgstr ""
"Scanne deine Website nach verwaisten Elementen, die Probleme verursachen "
"könnten."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1017,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1017
msgid "Builder capabilities"
msgstr "Builder-Berechtigungen"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1021,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1021
msgid ""
"Set up your own capabilities with the exact permissions you want to allow. "
"Then assign it to specific user roles from the \"Builder Access\" dropdown "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Lege deine eigenen Berechtigungen mit genau den Zugriffsrechten fest, die du "
"erlauben möchtest. Weise sie dann bestimmten Benutzerrollen über das "
"Dropdown-Menü „Builder-Zugriff“ unten zu."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1110,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1110
msgid "Add new capability"
msgstr "Neue Berechtigung hinzufügen"

#. translators: %s = article link
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1123,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1123
msgid ""
"Set %s per user role. To define access for a specific user edit the user "
"profile directly."
msgstr ""
"Lege %s pro Benutzerrolle fest. Um den Zugriff für einen bestimmten Benutzer "
"festzulegen, bearbeite direkt das Benutzerprofil."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1123,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1123
msgid "builder access"
msgstr "Builder-Zugriff"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1161,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1161
msgid ""
"This user role has %s capability, and therefore full builder access. "
"Effectively overriding this setting."
msgstr ""
"Diese Benutzerrolle hat die Berechtigung %s und damit vollen Builder-"
"Zugriff. Dies überschreibt effektiv diese Einstellung."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1178,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1178
msgid "Template screenshots"
msgstr "Template-Screenshots"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1179,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1179
msgid ""
"Enable to automatically generate template screenshots on every builder save, "
"view them, and use the bulk generate button in the template manager."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um automatisch Template-Screenshots bei jedem Speichern des "
"Builders zu generieren, sie anzusehen und die Schaltfläche zur "
"Massengenerierung im Template-Manager zu nutzen."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1188,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1188
msgid "Delete screenshots"
msgstr "Screenshots löschen"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1193,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1193
msgid "Template manager thumbnail height"
msgstr "Höhe des Template-Manager-Vorschaubilds"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1195,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1195
msgid ""
"Set a specific height for your template manager thumbnails in the builder. "
"Thumbnails exceeding this height auto-scroll on mouseover."
msgstr ""
"Lege eine bestimmte Höhe für deine Template-Manager-Thumbnails im Builder "
"fest. Thumbnails, die diese Höhe überschreiten, scrollen beim Überfahren mit "
"der Maus automatisch."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1201,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1206,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1211,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1201,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1206,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1211
msgid "Template thumbnail column"
msgstr "Template-Vorschaubild-Spalte"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1202,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1202
msgid ""
"Enable to show the template thumbnail column under %s, displaying the "
"featured image or screenshot."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um die Template-Thumbnail-Spalte unter %s anzuzeigen, die "
"das Titelbild oder den Screenshot zeigt."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1218,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1218
msgid "Disable default templates"
msgstr "Standard-Templates deaktivieren"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1219,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1219
msgid ""
"If no template conditions are set Bricks shows published templates (header, "
"footer, etc.) on the frontend of your site. Select this setting to disable "
"this behavior. Make sure to set template conditions instead."
msgstr ""
"Wenn keine Template-Bedingungen festgelegt sind, zeigt Bricks "
"veröffentlichte Templates (Header, Footer, etc.) im Frontend deiner Website "
"an. Wähle diese Einstellung, um dieses Verhalten zu deaktivieren. Stelle "
"sicher, stattdessen Template-Bedingungen festzulegen."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1224,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1224
msgid "Public templates"
msgstr "Öffentliche Templates"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1225,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1225
msgid ""
"Enable to make your templates public and viewable by anyone online. Disable "
"to allow only logged-in users to view your templates."
msgstr ""
"Aktiviere dies, um deine Templates öffentlich und für jeden online sichtbar "
"zu machen. Deaktiviere es, um nur eingeloggten Benutzern die Ansicht deiner "
"Templates zu erlauben."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1230,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1230
msgid "My templates access"
msgstr "Zugriff auf meine Templates"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1231,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1231
msgid ""
"Allow other sites to browse and insert your templates from their template "
"library. Restrict template access via \"Whitelist URLs\" and \"Password "
"Protection\" settings below."
msgstr ""
"Erlaube anderen Websites, deine Templates in ihrer Template-Bibliothek zu "
"durchsuchen und einzufügen. Beschränke den Template-Zugriff über die "
"Einstellungen „Whitelist-URLs“ und „Passwortschutz“ unten."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1235,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1235
msgid "Whitelist URLs"
msgstr "Whitelist-URLs"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1237,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1237
msgid ""
"Only grant access to your templates to the websites entered above. One URL "
"per line."
msgstr ""
"Gewähre nur den oben eingetragenen Websites Zugriff auf deine Templates. "
"Eine URL pro Zeile."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1243,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1243
msgid "Password protect your templates."
msgstr "Schütze deine Templates mit einem Passwort."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1247,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1247
msgid "Exclude templates"
msgstr "Templates ausschließen"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1269,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1269
msgid "Select templates to exclude from remote template access."
msgstr ""
"Wähle Templates aus, die vom Remote-Template-Zugriff ausgeschlossen werden "
"sollen."

