#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1884,
#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1888,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1897,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1901
msgid "Cache query loops"
msgstr "Abfrageschleifen cachen"

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1889,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1902
msgid ""
"Set to improve performance by caching query loops. This is particularly "
"useful when your query loop arguments remain relatively unchanged. For "
"optimal functionality, ensure that server object caching is enabled for "
"persistent caching. Disable this setting if you experience any unexpected "
"query results."
msgstr ""
"Eingestellt, um die Leistung durch Caching von Abfrageschleifen zu "
"verbessern. Dies ist besonders nützlich, wenn die Argumente deiner "
"Abfrageschleife relativ unverändert bleiben. Für eine optimale "
"Funktionalität stelle sicher, dass das Server-Objekt-Caching für "
"persistentes Caching aktiviert ist. Deaktiviere diese Einstellung, wenn du "
"unerwartete Abfrageergebnisse erhältst."

#: ../build/bricks/includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1895,
#: ../includes/admin/admin-screen-settings.php:1908
msgid "Disable class chaining"
msgstr "Klassen-Verkettung deaktivieren"

